00:57:10,570 --> 00:57:11,980
that I have a disadvantage.

847
00:57:12,380 --> 00:57:14,240
I'll get better if I try it a few more times.

848
00:57:14,440 --> 00:57:15,640
That previous humiliation...

849
00:57:17,400 --> 00:57:18,460
I'll give it back to you.

850
00:57:32,780 --> 00:57:33,160
God.

851
00:57:35,340 --> 00:57:36,600
MY STRAWBERRY

852
00:57:40,130 --> 00:57:41,830
Hi. Hello?

853
00:57:42,230 --> 00:57:43,060
Hello, Ha Jin.

854
00:57:43,460 --> 00:57:45,530
What? Why are you so out of breath?

855
00:57:45,930 --> 00:57:46,630
No...

856
00:57:47,530 --> 00:57:48,540
I was playing a game.

857
00:57:48,640 --> 00:57:51,330
A game? You said you'd never play.

858
00:57:51,830 --> 00:57:54,910
My boss wanted to play with me.

859
00:57:56,010 --> 00:57:57,270
Is that the director?

860
00:57:58,470 --> 00:58:00,800
Yes. Really, why are you calling?

861
00:58:00,900 --> 00:58:03,000
I wanted you to come here for dinner,

862
00:58:03,100 --> 00:58:03,800
but that's okay.

863
00:58:03,900 --> 00:58:05,960
Or take it with you.

864
00:58:06,660 --> 00:58:07,100
What?

865
00:58:15,120 --> 00:58:16,340
What is the name of that restaurant?

866
00:58:16,740 --> 00:58:17,970
Maybe I know her.

867
00:58:18,870 --> 00:58:20,350
Probably not.

868
00:58:21,050 --> 00:58:22,380
It is located in a remote area.

869
00:58:22,480 --> 00:58:23,810
Maybe that's why he doesn't have customers.

870
00:58:23,910 --> 00:58:24,970
But the food is good.

871
00:58:25,070 --> 00:58:25,990
Are you sure?

872
00:58:26,790 --> 00:58:28,520
I have very high standards.

873
00:58:29,120 --> 00:58:31,490
So eat at home. I'll go alone.

874
00:58:34,090 --> 00:58:35,110
I'll try it.

875
00:58:56,650 --> 00:58:58,090
I can do it myself.

876
00:58:58,290 --> 00:59:00,530
How hard did you try to defeat me?

877
00:59:03,400 --> 00:59:05,460
I can ask you the same thing.

878
00:59:13,120 --> 00:59:13,820
Done.

879
00:59:44,100 --> 00:59:45,750
- Ha Jin, I'm in front of... - Don't come here.

880
00:59:47,350 --> 00:59:49,040
- What? - There's a Black Dragon.

881
01:00:14,810 --> 01:00:18,000
MY DEAREST NEMEZIS